Train YOLO model with new PPE classes
Update app/ppe_detector.py
Add new violation types to configuration
Update email templates

Custom Email Templates
Edit the email templates in app/email_service.py:
   Copied EMAIL_TEMPLATES = {
    'violation_alert': 'templates/emails/violation_alert.html',
    'compliance_report': 'templates/emails/compliance_report.html'
} üîß Troubleshooting
Common Issues
Camera not detected:
   Copied # Check available cameras
python -c "import cv2; print([cv2.VideoCapture(i).isOpened() for i in range(10)])" Email not sending:

Verify SMTP credentials
Check firewall settings
Enable less secure apps (for Gmail)

Model not loading:

Download the model file from releases
Check file permissions
Verify model path in configuration

